Research Interests
My main research focus is on developing new algorithms and optimization techniques for large-scale
machine learning problems. Currently, I am working on the following problems:
• Adversarial machine learning.
• Fast and scalable algorithms for large-scale training.
• Fast Prediction and Model Compression for big ML models.
• Recommender systems.
• AutoML: neural architecture search and hyper-parameter tuning.
